---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Dental Sealants" 
  category="Preventive Care"
  description="Dental sealants are a thin layer of plastic placed on the chewing surfaces of your molars at the back of your mouth to prevent cavities."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516574187841-cb9cc2ca948b?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Cavity Prevention Made Easy</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        Dental sealants are a thin layer of plastic placed on the chewing surfaces of your molars 
        at the back of your mouth â€“ which are usually the teeth you use to chew your food. 
        This simple preventive treatment provides powerful protection against cavities.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      What Are Dental Sealants?
    </h2>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Dental sealants are protective, tooth-colored coatings applied to the chewing surfaces 
            of back teeth (molars and premolars). They act as a barrier, protecting these cavity-prone 
            areas from plaque and bacteria that cause tooth decay.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Why Molars Need Extra Protection</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Deep grooves and pits trap food and bacteria</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Difficult to clean with regular brushing</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Experience heavy chewing forces</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span>Most susceptible to decay in children and teens</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="w-72 h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200/30 rounded-lg shadow-md flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Who Benefits Most from Sealants?
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Children -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-3">Children (Ages 6-14)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
          The ideal candidates as permanent molars emerge. Sealants applied soon after eruption 
          provide maximum protection during cavity-prone years.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-lg p-3">
          <p class="text-xs text-blue-800">
            <strong>Best timing:</strong> First molars at age 6, second molars at age 12
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Teens -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-500 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 mb-3">Teenagers</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
          High-risk period due to dietary habits and sometimes inconsistent oral hygiene. 
          Sealants provide crucial protection during these vulnerable years.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-green-100 rounded-lg p-3">
          <p class="text-xs text-green-800">
            <strong>Benefits:</strong> 80% reduction in cavities for up to 2 years, 50% for up to 4 years
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Adults -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-500 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-3">Adults at Risk</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
          Adults with deep grooves who haven't had cavities in their molars can still benefit. 
          Also recommended for those with dry mouth or high cavity risk.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-purple-100 rounded-lg p-3">
          <p class="text-xs text-purple-800">
            <strong>Candidates:</strong> Cavity-free molars with deep pits and fissures
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      The Sealant Application Process
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Tooth Preparation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              The tooth is thoroughly cleaned and dried. Any existing decay is removed if present. 
              The chewing surface is prepared with a mild etching solution to help the sealant bond.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-primary-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>No anesthesia needed:</strong> The process is completely painless and non-invasive
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-900 font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Sealant Application</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              The liquid sealant material is carefully painted onto the chewing surface, flowing into 
              all the grooves and pits. The material is then hardened using a special curing light.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-accent-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Quick process:</strong> Each tooth takes only a few minutes to seal
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Final Check & Polish</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              We check the bite to ensure the sealant doesn't interfere with chewing, make any necessary 
              adjustments, and polish the surface. You can eat normally right after the appointment.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-primary-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Immediate results:</strong> Protection starts working right away
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Sealant Benefits & Effectiveness
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Proven Protection</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">80%</span>
                </div>
                <span class="font-semibold">Cavity Reduction</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Sealants prevent 80% of cavities in back teeth for the first 2 years after application
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">50%</span>
                </div>
                <span class="font-semibold">Long-term Protection</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Continue to protect against 50% of cavities for up to 4 years
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">9x</span>
                </div>
                <span class="font-semibold">Greater Protection</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Children with sealants are 9 times less likely to develop cavities in sealed teeth
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Additional Benefits</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Cost-effective:</strong> Much less expensive than treating cavities</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Painless:</strong> No drilling or tooth removal required</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Quick application:</strong> Entire appointment typically under 30 minutes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Invisible protection:</strong> Clear or tooth-colored material</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Long-lasting:</strong> Can last many years with proper care</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Repairable:</strong> Can be touched up or reapplied if needed</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Caring for Your Sealants
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-700 mb-4">Do's</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Brush and floss regularly as usual</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Use fluoride toothpaste and mouthwash</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Attend regular dental checkups</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Eat a balanced diet low in sugary snacks</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Have sealants checked and maintained regularly</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-700 mb-4">Avoid</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Chewing on ice or hard objects</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Biting fingernails or pen caps</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Using teeth as tools</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Excessive grinding or clenching</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Sticky candies that can pull off sealants</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Sealants vs. Traditional Cavity Treatment
    </h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12">
      <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md">
        <thead class="bg-primary-100">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold text-primary-900">Aspect</th>
            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-green-700">Sealants (Prevention)</th>
            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-red-700">Fillings (Treatment)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
          <tr>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium">Cost</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-green-600">$30-60 per tooth</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">$150-400+ per filling</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
